00:04:55.952 --> 00:04:57.745
'Aku harus mencekik
orang tua ini.'

00:04:57.829 --> 00:04:59.245
“Dia punya banyak pertanyaan.”

00:04:59.370 --> 00:05:00.662
'Aku harus mematahkan wajahnya.'

