apa yang Preesha ingat?

00:05:23.328 --> 00:05:24.745
'Aku ditakdirkan.'

00:05:25.036 --> 00:05:26.787
'Dia telah menjebakku di sini'

00:05:26.912 --> 00:05:28.620
