Kami akan pergi ke
rumah Arjun Verma besok.

00:10:46.412 --> 00:10:47.620
Ke alamatnya di Delhi.

00:10:47.829 --> 00:10:49.537
Oke.  Sampai jumpa besok.

00:10:50.162 --> 00:10:51.704
Sudah terlambat.
Kamu sebaiknya pergi.

00:10:51.787 --> 00:10:52.953
